{{#cargo_declare:_table=loot_drops|item=String|quantity=String}}
This template is used on NPC pages to list item drops. It's used in combination with [[Template:List Loot Sources]] on Item pages.

LootDrop works similar to [[Template:ItemFrame]] in terms of linking, but also records the drop in the Cargo table <code>loot_drops</code> (and keeps the legacy <code>Drops loot ...</code> category).

List Loot Sources queries Cargo to dynamically fetch and link to all NPC pages that use LootDrop for the item.
